1
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:05,260
Hey, Rick, I have to make a project for
the science fair this weekend.

2
00:00:05,480 --> 00:00:06,836
You think you could help me out?

3
00:00:06,860 --> 00:00:07,180
Whatever.

4
00:00:07,380 --> 00:00:11,420
Well, I mean, traditionally, science fairs
are a father-son thing.

5
00:00:11,740 --> 00:00:14,520
Well, scientifically, traditions are an
idiot thing.

6
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:18,060
Morty, I think it would be fun for you to
work on a science project with your dad.

7
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:25,240
Yeah, Dad, why don't we do it together?

8
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:25,760
Yes!

9
00:00:26,060 --> 00:00:27,900
You backed the right horse on this one,
son.

10
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:29,963
We'll get out the
crayons, brew some coffee,

11
00:00:29,964 --> 00:00:32,661
and knock this thing
out in two or three days.

12
00:00:33,315 --> 00:00:34,600
What is my purpose?

13
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:35,800
Pass the butter.

14
00:00:39,015 --> 00:00:40,080
Thank you.

15
00:00:42,445 --> 00:00:44,280
Dad, I need a ride to work.

16
00:00:44,709 --> 00:00:46,300
Maybe Rick can give you a ride.

17
00:00:46,605 --> 00:00:48,700
I'm helping Morty with science.

18
00:00:48,855 --> 00:00:49,600
I'm busy.

19
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,600
Doing what?

20
00:00:50,760 --> 00:00:52,140
Uh, anything else?

21
00:00:53,425 --> 00:00:54,840
What is my purpose?

22
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:56,100
You pass butter.

23
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,620
Oh, my God.

24
00:00:58,621 --> 00:01:00,140
Yeah, welcome to the club, pal.

25
00:01:00,141 --> 00:01:01,381
Yeah, welcome to the club, pal.

